Our goal is to be around for a really long time

00:28:47.839 --> 00:28:51.760
so that we can tackle problems that potentially take decades to solve.

00:28:53.760 --> 00:28:59.040
So how do we do that? Well, first of all, we're a PBC and a B Corp. What does that mean?

00:28:59.920 --> 00:29:04.800
Well, if you're going to like traditional C Corp or LLC, basically the fundamental

00:29:04.800 --> 00:29:11.040
responsibility encoded in the corporate charter is to maximize value for shareholders, to make

00:29:11.040 --> 00:29:16.959
as much money as possible for the people that own some part of your company. The idea of the B Corp

