00:29:22.400 --> 00:29:27.439
some of the company, and that maybe the best thing to do is not just to optimize the amount of money.

00:29:29.040 --> 00:29:33.119
And so the idea of the B Corp is to recognize that there are other communities like the broader

00:29:33.119 --> 00:29:40.400
open-source data science community that we really care about. And it's like that caring,

00:29:40.400 --> 00:29:44.400
that importance is fundamentally baked into our charter as a company.

00:29:47.520 --> 00:29:53.439
The other component of this is like we want to remain independent, which means we're closely

00:29:53.439 --> 00:29:59.280
held, we're private, we're never going to IPO, we're never going to be acquired by someone.

00:29:59.280 --> 00:30:05.599
Our goal is to be independent, and we do that by being profitable. And we're profitable because

00:30:05.599 --> 00:30:11.680
we sell software. So kind of four main things we sell. Connect, which really helps kind of get the

