do we need Shiny for Python, I think, is the concise way. Yeah, that's a really good question.

00:49:19.840 --> 00:49:25.120
I think it comes down to this idea of reactivity. Like, if you're creating something simple,

00:49:25.120 --> 00:49:30.560
